---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Opey Theophilus" class="profile-photo" />

        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">5+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years of Study</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">20+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Projects Completed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">3+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Competitions Entered</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Architecture is the<br/><em>art of possibility.</em></h2>
        <p>
          I'm Opey Theophilus, a third year architecture student with a strong passion for architectural visualization and computational design.
        </p>
        <p>
          I enjoy using visuals to communicate design concepts with clarity while exploring computational methods to approach problems with innovation and precision.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am eager to bring these skills into a professional environment and contribute meaningfully to design projects.
        </p>
        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="#projects" class="link-arrow">View Projects <span>→</span></a>
          <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="link-arrow">Download CV <span>→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about { background: var(--off-white); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content .section-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .link-arrow {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--black);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--black);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .link-arrow span { transition: transform 0.2s; display: inline-block; }
  .link-arrow:hover span { transform: translateX(4px); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
